name: MultiWorld: Survival
description:
Out of nowhere, for unknown reasons, you ended up in the unidentified world where everything seems to be stunning and beautiful, but nothing is perfect. Are you ready to explore and face the unknown? Is there a way out to your previous world and life?

The game is in early access, you may encounter bugs. 

Gameplay time ~30mins. (more content soon!)

Version 0.10       

Discord: https://discord.gg/dyytdYyrmd

Share with us your thoughts, opinions, and ideas. :)

Have fun!

The game is FREE but you can support us by giving a tip.
